							</a>
							<p><a href="http://iath.virginia.edu" title="Institute for Advanced Technology in the Humanities">The Institute for Advanced
									Technology in the Humanities</a> at the University of Virginia hosts Kerameikos.org</p>
						</div>-->
					</div>

				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</xsl:template>
</xsl:stylesheet>
